### **2. main_APIWatchTower**  
**Description:**  
A script that monitors the availability and latency of any list of endpoints.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# APIWatchTower - HTTP Uptime & Latency Tracker

APIWatchTower gives devs real-time visibility into the performance of their APIs and services.

## Features
- Tracks response codes & timing  
- Logs to console or file  
- Handles timeouts gracefully  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/main_APIWatchTower.git
cd main_APIWatchTower
python monitor.py
